{\cf1\f1\fs22 1}The {\scaps Lord}\uc1\u8217*s message to Hosea son of Beeri during the reigns of Kings Uzziah, Jotham, Ahaz, and Hezekiah of Judah and during the reign of King Jeroboam, son of Joash of Israel.
